#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""dot - front door for this dotfiles repo.

One engine, two front-ends:
  * scriptable CLI: dot deploy [modules...] [--dry-run], status, diff, snapshot, sync
  * interactive TUI: `dot` with no args (curses; tabs + checkboxes + drift markers)

The module registry below is the structure that used to be hard-coded as a
linear deploy.sh. Each module is an ordered list of typed steps; deploy.sh and
snapshot.sh are now thin shims that exec this tool.
"""

